com.qtplaf.library.trading.data

Class DelegateDataList

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.qtplaf.library.trading.data.DataList
      • com.qtplaf.library.trading.data.DelegateDataList

  • public class DelegateDataList
extends DataList
    A delegate data list, used when a copy of the datalist with a different data info is required. Can access a part of the data indexes.
    Author:
    Miquel Sas
